{"tid":2284682,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印媒指中印正制定方案 結束邊境軍事對峙 包括設緩沖區及撤走武器等","createTime":"2020-11-13T13:17:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T18:44:37.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cb76605688c4a00248fb0223988f7805950ae88a","tid":2284682,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T13:17:58.000Z","msg":"印媒指中印正制定方案 結束在拉達克的軍事對峙<br />\n<br />\n印度傳媒引述政府官員說，中國同印度正制定方案，結束在拉達克地區的軍事對峙，包括在班公湖設立禁止巡邏的緩沖區，撤走在區內的坦克及火炮，使用無人機核實兩軍的撤軍行動；雙方正進行內部討論，兩軍指揮官將在一周內再度會面，商討如何落實兩軍脫離接觸。印度國防部及外交部拒絕對報道置評。<br />\n<br />\n中印兩軍6月在拉達克地區的加勒萬河谷，爆發激烈肢體衝突，印軍有20人喪生，中國部隊亦有傷亡，兩軍其後增兵區內對峙，中印關係跌至冰點。目前拉達克地區的溫度，降至零度以下18度，兩軍軍長上星期五曾會面，商討緩和邊境局勢。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2366170\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2366170&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIuSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=06a6aa7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2366170</a>"},{"pid":"8822965f76c902759aa822d00910f01c17d70118","tid":2284682,"uid":316927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T13:19:06.000Z","msg":"信就on9"},{"pid":"d8623aaea0aad2b13ec824edb07dc524b5b1e55b","tid":2284682,"uid":151074,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T13:59:09.000Z","msg":"加速師已經準備好偷襲印印"},{"pid":"46792a810541214890ea2374d38f40e1d6fe8807","tid":2284682,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T14:00:12.000Z","msg":"見侵侵弱勢就縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4305b097149fad948ff4f80bd8460f04d3bb9c20","tid":2284682,"uid":12410,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T16:07:54.000Z","msg":"冬天啦 邊個守 邊個死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00465fe14f5a23c2fc53cd388a3fd2c81b8f67a7","tid":2284682,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T17:17:20.000Z","msg":"支媒唔撚信 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ffcdfbae8c64b3231a0098b402325f9f3db604f","tid":2284682,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T18:37:12.000Z","msg":"屌晒你地老母！<br />\n明明班公錯湖係要塞 點會守唔到！<br />\n即刻同我返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a114488296c242584a7fb1bd6e0a1cc4de80d293","tid":2284682,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4305b097149fad948ff4f80bd8460f04d3bb9c20","tid":2284682,"uid":12410,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T16:07:54.000Z","msg":"冬天啦 邊個守 邊個死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T18:44:37.000Z","msg":"印度🇮🇳方易補給 中方就難講"}]}